query:
SELECT EXISTS(
            SELECT 1 FROM tenant_workspace_members twm
            JOIN users u ON twm.email = u.email
            WHERE twm.tenant_workspace_id = $1 AND u.id = $2
        ) OR EXISTS(
            SELECT 1 FROM organization_member_metadata
            WHERE organization_id = $1 AND user_id = $2
        ) AS "exists!"
